Each folder here contains a Solr core configuration.

Deploy these using symlinks from your Solr home:

cd /srv/solr/example/solr # == Solr home
cd api/conf # "api" core configuration
ln -s /home/api/api.npolar.no/solr/api/schema.xml

The idea is to keep just the essential / changed-from-default Solr configuration in version control,
to allow for easier future updates of Solr.

